cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is primarily focused on image smoothing, which is a task in computer vision, making cs.CV the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a deep learning approach using texture and structure prediction networks, which falls under the scope of cs.AI and cs.LG. Additionally, the paper involves generating a large dataset, which could be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.GR (Graphics).
